### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Leather E-Commerce — API Tests
### Usage: Open in VS Code with the "REST Client" extension (humao.rest-client)
###        Hit "Send Request" above any request to run it.
###
### Workflow:
###   1. Health check to confirm server is up
###   2. Register a user → copy accessToken into @accessToken
###   3. Register/login an admin → copy accessToken into @adminToken
###   4. Create a category → copy id into @categoryId
###   5. Create a product → copy slug into @productSlug and id into @productId
###   6. Run cart tests (requires @accessToken and @productId)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

