### CATEGORIES — Public
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 28. Get all categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories

###

### 29. Get category by slug — valid
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/wallets

###

### 30. Get category by slug — not found (should return 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/this-does-not-exist


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### CATEGORIES — Admin
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 31. Create category — valid (copy returned id into @categoryId above)
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Wallets",
  "slug": "wallets"
}

###

### 32. Create category — duplicate slug (should return 409)
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Wallets Duplicate",
  "slug": "wallets"
}

###

### 33. Create category — missing name (should return 422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "slug": "bags"
}

###

### 34. Create category — invalid slug format (should return 422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Bags",
  "slug": "Bags With Spaces!!"
}

###

### 35. Create second category (copy id into @categoryId above)
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Bags",
  "slug": "bags"
}

###

### 36. Create category — no auth token (should return 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sneaky Category",
  "slug": "sneaky"
}

###

### 37. Create category — customer token, not admin (should return 403)
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "name": "Customer Attempt",
  "slug": "customer-attempt"
}

###

### 38. Update category — valid
PUT {{baseUrl}}/categories/wallets
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Premium Wallets"
}

###

### 39. Update category — slug not found (should return 404)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/categories/non-existent-slug
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Ghost"
}

###

### 40. Update category — no auth (should return 401)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/categories/wallets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sneaky Update"
}

###

### 41. Delete category — valid
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/categories/bags
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 42. Delete category — already deleted (should return 404)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/categories/bags
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 43. Delete category — no auth (should return 401)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/categories/wallets


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### PRODUCTS — Public
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 44. Get all products — default pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/products

###

### 45. Get products — custom page and limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?page=1&limit=6

###

### 46. Get products — search by keyword
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?search=leather

###

### 47. Get products — filter by category ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?category={{categoryId}}

###

### 48. Get products — filter by gender
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?gender=men

###

### 49. Get products — search + category + gender combined
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?search=wallet&category={{categoryId}}&gender=unisex

###

### 50. Get products — invalid page (should return 422)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?page=0

###

### 51. Get products — limit over 50 (should return 422)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?limit=999

###

### 52. Get products — invalid category UUID format (should return 422)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?category=not-a-uuid

###

### 53. Get product by slug — valid (update @productSlug above first)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productSlug}}

###

### 54. Get product by slug — not found (should return 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/this-product-does-not-exist


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### PRODUCTS — Admin
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 55. Create product — valid (copy slug into @productSlug and id into @productId)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Classic Bifold Wallet",
  "slug": "classic-bifold-wallet",
  "description": "A slim, handcrafted genuine leather bifold wallet with 6 card slots.",
  "price": 49.99,
  "discountPrice": 39.99,
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "stock": 100,
  "isFeatured": true,
  "gender": "men",
  "images": [],
  "tags": ["wallet", "leather", "bifold", "slim"]
}

###

### 56. Create product — missing required fields (should return 422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Incomplete Product"
}

###

### 57. Create product — invalid slug format (should return 422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Bad Slug",
  "slug": "Bad Slug With Capitals",
  "description": "Test",
  "price": 10,
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "stock": 5
}

###

### 58. Create product — negative price (should return 422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Negative Price",
  "slug": "negative-price",
  "description": "Test",
  "price": -10,
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "stock": 5
}

###

### 59. Create product — discount price higher than price (should return 422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Bad Discount",
  "slug": "bad-discount",
  "description": "Test",
  "price": 20,
  "discountPrice": 50,
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "stock": 5
}

###

### 60. Create product — invalid categoryId UUID (should return 422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Bad Category",
  "slug": "bad-category",
  "description": "Test",
  "price": 20,
  "categoryId": "not-a-uuid",
  "stock": 5
}

###

### 61. Create product — categoryId not found in DB (should return 422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Ghost Category",
  "slug": "ghost-category",
  "description": "Test",
  "price": 20,
  "categoryId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "stock": 5
}

###

### 62. Create product — no auth (should return 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sneaky Product",
  "slug": "sneaky-product",
  "description": "Test",
  "price": 10,
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "stock": 1
}

###

### 63. Create product — customer token (should return 403)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "name": "Customer Product",
  "slug": "customer-product",
  "description": "Test",
  "price": 10,
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "stock": 1
}

###

### 64. Update product — valid partial update
PUT {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productSlug}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "price": 44.99,
  "stock": 80
}

###

### 65. Update product — not found (should return 404)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/products/ghost-product
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "price": 10
}

###

### 66. Update product — no auth (should return 401)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productSlug}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 1
}

###

### 67. Delete product — valid
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productSlug}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 68. Delete product — already deleted (should return 404)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productSlug}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 69. Delete product — no auth (should return 401)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productSlug}}


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### CART — all routes require auth (Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}})
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 70. Get cart — valid (empty on first run)
GET {{baseUrl}}/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 71. Get cart — no auth (should return 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/cart

###

### 72. Add item to cart — valid (use a real @productId above)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "quantity": 2
}

###

### 73. Add same item again — should increment quantity, not duplicate
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "quantity": 1
}

###

### 74. Add to cart — invalid productId UUID (should return 422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "productId": "not-a-valid-uuid",
  "quantity": 1
}

###

### 75. Add to cart — product not found (should return 404)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "productId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "quantity": 1
}

###

### 76. Add to cart — quantity 0 (should return 422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "quantity": 0
}

###

### 77. Add to cart — quantity exceeds stock (should return 422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "quantity": 99999
}

###

### 78. Add to cart — no auth (should return 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "quantity": 1
}

###

### 79. Update cart item quantity — valid
PUT {{baseUrl}}/cart/{{productId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "quantity": 5
}

###

### 80. Update cart item — item not in cart (should return 404)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/cart/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "quantity": 3
}

###

### 81. Update cart item — quantity 0 (should return 422)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/cart/{{productId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "quantity": 0
}

###

### 82. Update cart item — quantity exceeds stock (should return 422)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/cart/{{productId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "quantity": 99999
}

###

### 83. Update cart item — no auth (should return 401)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/cart/{{productId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 2
}

###

### 84. Remove specific item from cart — valid
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart/{{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 85. Remove item — not in cart (should return 404)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 86. Remove item — no auth (should return 401)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart/{{productId}}

###

### 87. Clear entire cart — valid
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 88. Clear cart — already empty (should return 404)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 89. Clear cart — no auth (should return 401)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart
